data.description: Beautiful 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths home located in the sought after neighborhood of Steeplechase in Northeast Suffolk. 1 mile from Bennetts Creek Park. The community is great for family fun with a pool, clubhouse and trails. The AC unit is approx 3 ½ yrs old, and the water heater is approx 2 ½ yrs old. Hardwood, LVP, and tile floors throughout. Large primary bedroom with sitting room and large walk-in closet. Large tub and separate shower in primary bath. Large deck in back.
